    <Service>
        <name>Online Peer Review Tool</name>
        <abstract_desc>This is an on-line tool to homogenize review efforts for smaller datasets in either PDS3 or PDS4 label formats.</abstract_desc>
        <url>https://atmos.nmsu.edu/elsa/review/</url>
        <service_type>Service</service_type>
        <interface_type>GUI</interface_type>
        <category>Validation</category>
        <supported_operating_system_note>All browsers are supported.</supported_operating_system_note>
        <description>This review form is used to allow reviewers to focus their efforts to answer several important questions about the data under review.  The mechanics of the web form aid in cross-communication between the Node, the reviewer and the data provider.  Once the reviewer has completed the form, and hit the submit button, the web form is converted to a PDF and mailed to the node representative and the data provider.  The reviews are collected and then distributed to all reviewers and data providers for discussion during a telecon.</description>
    </Service>
